    The image should have a slide-in animation (left to right) when visible.
    
    Right Column (Content Block)
    
    Editable heading/title (H2) – bold and prominent.
    
    Editable paragraph description (multi-line).
    
    A list of 4 items each containing:
    2 item in one row
    Small icon upload (SVG/PNG).
    
    Bold text label next to icon.
    
    A final bold text line at the bottom (separate field in schema).
    
    Responsive rules:
    
    On mobile → image on top, content block below.
    
    Maintain padding and spacing so text/icons remain aligned.
    
