    Image upload
    
    Text fields for Name + Designation
    
    Title (H2)
    
    Description (Richtext)
    
    4 Repeater Blocks → (Icon + Text)
    
    Bottom bold text field
    
    Styling:
    
    Colors, spacing, typography should be customizable from schema (at least heading color, icon color, and overlay background).
    
